        "name": "Spectral Strike (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Flayed Knight swings its spectral blade at a target, its ethereal form allowing the weapon to pass through armor and resistance. It makes a melee attack, dealing D4 Slashing damage on a hit that ignores all Armor.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Haunting Grasp (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Flayed Knight extends its ghostly hand toward a target, attempting to drain their life force. It deals D6 Necrotic damage on a hit and regains Health equal to half the damage dealt.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 5,
        "endDie": 6,
        "name": "Vengeful Cleave (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Flayed Knight swings its blade in a wide arc, attempting to cleave through multiple targets within its reach. It makes a melee attack against two creatures, dealing D6 Slashing damage to each target. If either attack hits and reduces a target to 0 Toughness, the Flayed Knight regains Health equal to half the damage dealt.</p></div>"
      }
    ],
    "description": "<div><p>Flayed Knights are a horrifying apparition of a once-glorious knight whose body has been grotesquely flayed and stripped of its flesh. Its skeletal form is adorned with the tattered remnants of once-regal armor, now stained with the memories of its violent demise. Brandishing its rusted and blood-stained blade, the Flayed Knight unleashes unholy fury upon any who dare to cross its path. Its spectral weapon cleaves through flesh and bone with ease, leaving behind a trail of death.</p></div>",
